---
description: Use project venv before running Python/terminal commands
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---

Before running any Python or install commands in this project, enable the virtual environment:

- **Unix/macOS:** `source .venv/bin/activate`
- Or run commands via: `.venv/bin/python`, `.venv/bin/pip`, etc.

Ensure `.venv` is activated (or use its binaries) before executing project commands.
